Package: EPIMOS
Type: Package
Title: Environmental Prediction and Imputation Modular Statistical System
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Francisco Richter [aut, cre] (<richtf@usi.ch>)
Maintainer: Francisco Richter <richtf@usi.ch>
Description: EPIMOS is a comprehensive framework designed to predict and impute missing environmental variables through a modular statistical approach. This package facilitates the preprocessing, modeling, and prediction of environmental data on both daily and yearly scales. It includes a data preprocessing module for handling raw environmental data, a prediction module for daily environmental variable predictions, and a building module for yearly updates to the prediction model.
